# Effective .dockerignore for root-context builds (python.Dockerfile, web.Dockerfile).
# Docker only reads .dockerignore from the build-context root, so it must live here.
# Excluding host node_modules/.venv is critical: their symlinks/binaries are
# host-specific and break the in-container install/build.
.git
.github
**/node_modules
node_modules
**/.venv
.venv
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/*.tsbuildinfo
infrastructure/terraform
**/.terraform
documentation
*.mp4
*.m4a
.vs
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
tfplan
*.tfplan
.env
**/.env
